{"word":"G5114 - τομώτερος - tomṓteros - tom-o'-ter-os - Sharper","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τομώτερος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tomṓteros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tom-o'-ter-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sharper</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கருக்குள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"sharper"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Compound of a derivative of the primary word <b>&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BC;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;</b> <b>temno&#x0304;</b> (to <i>cut</i>; more comprehensive or decisive than <a href=\"#/G2875 - κόπτω - kóptō - kop'-to/2875\">G2875</a>, as if by a <i>single</i> stroke; whereas that implies repeated blows, like <i>hacking</i>); <i>more keen:</i> - sharper.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}